
Title Exercise 0.4
Browser -> Server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note
Server -> Browser: Status Code 302
note right of Server: Asks browser to do a new HTTP GET request
Browser -> Server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/notes
Server -> Browser: HTML code
Browser -> Server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.css
Server -> Browser: CSS file "main.css"
Browser -> Server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.js
Server -> Browser: JavaScript file "main.js"
Browser -> Server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
Server -> Browser: data.json  raw data 




Title Exercise 0.5
Browser -> Server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/notes
Server -> Browser: HTML code
Browser -> Server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.css
Server -> Browser: CSS file "main.css"
Browser -> Server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.js
Server -> Browser: JavaScript file "main.js"
Browser -> Server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
Server -> Browser: data.json  raw data 
note left of Browser: Submit button pressed
note left of Browser: JS is executed and data is sent to server
Browser -> Server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note
Server -> Browser: status code 201
note left of Browser: submitted note is added to list without refreshing page



title Exercise 0.6
note left of Browser: Submit button pressed
note left of Browser: JS executes and prevents page reload
note left of Browser: JS executes event handler to add note to list
note left of Browser: data is sent to server as JSON type
Browser -> Server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note
Server -> Browser: status code 201

